<p itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question"><strong itemprop="name">How do I clean my Flawless&reg; Legs&trade; unit?</strong><br>
	<span itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><span itemprop="text">NOTE: Do NOT use Flawless&reg; Legs&trade; in the shower or submerge it in water to clean. While the unit is water resistant, it is NOT water-proof.
To clean your Flawless&reg; Legs&reg; unit, hold the main body of the shaver in one hand, and with the other hand, grip the tabs on the lower head and pull it away from the upper head.<br>
To remove hair clippings from the lower head, simply turn it over and gently shake it out over a trash can. Use the unit's cleaning brush to dislodge and remove any clippings stuck in the heads.</span></span>
</p>

<hr>

<p itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question"><strong itemprop="name">How often should I replace my Flawless&reg; Legs&trade; head?</strong><br>
	<span itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><span itemprop="text">Everyone is different. People with very long legs and a lot of hair will probably want to replace the head sooner than someone with shorter legs and lighter hair.
<br>
For average coverage area and hair density, replace the head every 3-4 months.</span></span>
</p>

